Here is a glimpse of the launch party of our latest collection - #SingaporeInspired curated by our fav homegrown brands. Everyone got a chance to see the pieces up close and personal and it's safe to say, they were blown away!

From classy floral jumpsuits inspired by the Peranakan prints curated by RSVP by Nykaa Fashion or beautiful sequin dresses that take their inspiration from the energetic nightlife of Singapore, the collection has become talk of the town. Chumbak with its quirky Singapore inspired designs printed on wall plates, bags and other accessories caught everyone's attention. And not to forget, The Souled Store pulled off the coolest looks for the fashion walk that were inspired by the Lion City, Year Of The Rabbit and more that happened to be everyone's favourite. 

If you haven't checked out the collection yet, head over to #LinkInBio and get ready to add some Singaporean style to your wardrobe.
